text: Javier Julián Castañeda Pomposo (born 7 October 1967) is a Mexican politician from the National Action Party. From 2000 to 2003 he served as Deputy of the LVIII Legislature of the Mexican Congress representing Baja California. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:People from Tijuana Category:Politicians from Baja California Category:Members of the Chamber of Deputies (Mexico) Category:National Action Party (Mexico) politicians Category:21st-century Mexican politicians Category:Members of the Congress of Baja California
title: Javier Castañeda Pomposo
